# Static CODEOWNERS.in rules — included verbatim in .github/CODEOWNERS
# between the default rule and generated per-resource rules.
# Edit this file (not CODEOWNERS) for static ownership rules.
# Regenerate CODEOWNERS after editing: make codeowners

# internal/common API client libraries
/internal/common/cloudintegrationsapi/**   @grafana/cloud-integrations
